shopifyProducts.title: Aalok Queen Bed In Silver and Warm Gray

This set features a unique headboard and footboard upholstered in velvet-like fabric, creating a plush and inviting atmosphere in your bedroom. Stay connected and organized with the modern conveniences of this set. The nightstand comes equipped with a built-in USB charger, allowing you to conveniently charge your devices while you sleep. The felt-lined top drawer protects your delicate items, keeping them safe and secure.

For those seeking extra storage options, the dresser features a hidden drawer, perfect for keeping your valuables or personal items out of sight. With ample storage and a sleek design, this bedroom set combines functionality and style seamlessly.

To ensure proper support and longevity of your mattress, a foundation is required for this set. Create a modern sanctuary in your bedroom with the Aalok Collection, where comfort and style meet harmoniously.

shopifyProducts.title: Aere Cool Gel Crystal Waterproof Mattress Protectors 10"-18" By Legget & Platt
shopifyProducts.description:
Aere Cool Gel Crystal Waterproof Mattress Protector

The Aere Crystal Gel Mattress Protector offers a breathable, 100% waterproof barrier designed to enhance the performance and longevity of your mattress. This protector not only shields your mattress from sweat, dead skin cells, liquid spills, dust mites, and mold buildup but also ensures a hygienic and comfortable sleeping environment. Over time, these factors can cause staining and potentially void your mattress warranty.

Features & Specifications:

  • Innovative Cooling Crystal Gel Fibers: Absorbs and dissipates heat away from the body for an ultra-cool sleep experience.
  • Revolutionary Tactile Technology 3D Fabric: Machine washable, promotes excellent airflow, and aids in moisture evaporation.
  • Dust Mite and Pet Dander Barrier: Provides a protective shield against common allergens.
  • Luxurious Stretch Fabric: Conforms to the mattress without altering its feel, ensuring a peaceful sleep.
  • Deep Corner Pockets: Stretch to fit the mattress securely and easily.

Available Sizes & Dimensions:

  • California King: 72" x 84" up to 18"

Shipping Details:

  • We provide free White Glove Delivery within Los Angeles County, including setup, removal of old bed, and packaging disposal.

Warranty:
10-year warranty against manufacturing defects.

Return Policy:
Due to its use as a personal item, protectors may not be returned.

shopifyProducts.title: Alaina 5Mm Beveled Mirror In Walnut

The Alaina 5Mm Beveled Mirror in Walnut is a sophisticated addition to any room, offering a timeless elegance that speaks to those with a refined taste. This dresser mirror, with its rich walnut finish, is crafted to complement a mature aesthetic, providing a sense of integrity and understated charm. Its clean, no-nonsense design ensures it stands out as a classic piece, impressing guests with its old-fashioned allure.

Constructed from solid wood and wood veneer, the Alaina mirror is not only visually appealing but also built to last. The beveled edges add a subtle depth and dimension, enhancing the mirror's reflective quality and providing a polished look. This mirror is perfect for those who appreciate traditional craftsmanship and desire a piece that seamlessly integrates into a variety of decor styles.

Whether placed in a bedroom, hallway, or living area, the Alaina 5 mm Beveled Mirror in Walnut serves as a functional and stylish focal point. Its durable construction and classic design make it a reliable choice for anyone looking to add a touch of elegance to their home.

This thoughtful detail not only adds a touch of luxury but also ensures that your valuables are kept in pristine condition. Designed for those who value both form and function, the Alaina Dresser With Support Rail In Walnut is a testament to quality craftsmanship. shopifyProducts.title: Alanis Dresser In Light Gray
shopifyProducts.description:
The Alanis Dresser in Light Gray by Furniture of America is a perfect blend of modern design and functional elegance. This dresser, part of the Alanis Collection, stands out with its unique mirror inserts that trim the drawer faces, creating a dynamic interplay with light that adds depth and interest to any room. The acrylic drawer pulls not only contribute to its contemporary style but also offer a touch of sophistication and ease of use.

Crafted from solid wood and other high-quality materials, this dresser is built to last. The felt-lined top drawers provide a soft, protective space for your delicate items, ensuring they remain scratch-free. The English dovetail drawer construction enhances durability, making this dresser a reliable choice for your storage needs.

Additionally, the Alanis Dresser features dedicated jewelry drawers, offering a convenient and organized solution for your accessories. The ball bearing metal glides ensure smooth and effortless drawer operation, adding to the overall user-friendly experience. This dresser is not just a piece of furniture; it's a stylish and practical addition to your home.

Features

  • Mirror inserts on drawer faces for added visual interest
  • Solid wood construction for durability
  • Felt-lined top drawers to protect delicate items
  • English dovetail drawer construction for strength
  • Dedicated jewelry drawers for organized storage
  • Ball bearing metal glides for smooth drawer operation
